# Test Rules

- Tests in this repo are high-value browser behavior checks, not just unit tests.
- Keep selectors and setup flows aligned with the runtime.
- When changing mechanics, prefer updating assertions to reflect intended behavior rather than weakening coverage.
- If a test becomes hard to maintain, simplify the setup, not the behavioral expectation.
